Detailed Description

FeatureItemContainerTableEntry feature_item_container_content_table: Reference to the configuration of the items of the FeatureItemContainer text: Text to be displayed in the menu icon_id: Icon to be displayed in the menu renderer_properties: defines how the items of the FeatureItemContainer has to be displayed Context_id: ContextID of this FeatureItemContainer
